  "instructions": [
    "cook buckwheat noodles according to package instructions. drain and set aside.",
    "heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. add onion, garlic, and ginger. cook until the onion is translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "add yuzu-cure, cumin, coriander, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper to the skillet. stir to combine.",
    "add cooked noodles to the skillet and stir to combine with the spice mixture.",
    "garnish with parsley and serve hot."
